query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total,
  SUM(CASE WHEN meetingId IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as from_fathom,
  SUM(CASE WHEN meetingId IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as manual
FROM tasks;
